reviewText: Awesome sauce

Well, it was great to see all the new art, and loved the strangely emotional scenes, but, the new English dub, like season 4, is more of a parody of the Japanese show.  It's all funny,  it's a comedy, but they change the words a lot for fan service. A good note is, the character are SO kawii.  PASTA!

I could never be dissapointed with the content of any season of hetalia. I bought this new from the new and used section cause money's a little tight so I picked the cheepest, deep discount DVD. And it got here today and the box was kinda banged up and warped ( as in the box is bending inward towards the case and bent edges ). And coming from a person who loves to keep my things nice and in the best condition possible, I'm deeply disappointed with the condition the box came in. BUT I could never dissapointed with hetalia. The stickers weren't bent and the bandana is perfect, bigger than I thought! I plan on inviting my friends over and having a screening! The disc is brand new and everything is perfect! Just a warning for other people who want their product in mint condition, think twice about that cheep price.

It arrived to UK 4 weeks after release, then the UK Royal Mail would not release it unless I paid duty and handling fees. So one DVD cost me nearly 40. I wish there were some clear warnings about these hidden charges.

The delivery was very fast, it came a few days early. The day after I received it in the mail I had to get a tooth drilled, so I had something to watch while I was in pain. The series is amazing, I love it and I've recommended it to a lot of people and all of my friends are addicted as well. Soon we will be having getting together to watch it. Simply put, I am the envy of all of my friends for being the only on to have it. The animation , music, voices and storylines are all very nice/beautiful.  All around it is more awesome than Prussia!

This by far is the greatest Hetalia season I have ever owned! I'm so glad I got it for a cheap price and it's in great condition! Also I ADORE the stickers it had! I couldn't be more happy with this product!

I am soo glad they come out with a new season but the animation is very different then the previous seasons. Also the translation from Japanese to English Is not the same. They have changed the lines of the characters when they translated it.  I hope they come out with a season 6. Because even after all these changes, I still get the same funny feelings I get with the other seasons!!
So damn funny! Great pop culture references and all new characters! I would much rather watch the English dub than the Japanese original!

I love hetalia, I've seen every episode and the beautiful world was AMAZING! My parents thought it was crap, and that i shouldn't waste money on "useless" stuff like this, and that i was gong to watch it once then be board with it, but i proved them wrong (again) . I watched the whole series multiple times (at least five), and I'm still not sick of it. It seems like they changed the art style in this one.... But either way, it's a great buy, and I'd recommend it to friends, family and total strangers! (however, i wouldn't recommend young (anyone under twelve) People to watch it, gets a bit inappropriate, but still awesome.

Hetalia has done it again! A new season is out, and this one, like the others, will have you laughing as you enjoy watching it with others (or even yourself)! So make yourself some popcorn, grab a blanket, turn off the lights and buckle on down for a marathon of fun, history, and STEREOTYPES! Just don't take this too seriously.

This anime is so funny! I didn't like the art style change at first but it quickly grew on me and I now adore it! All of the characters look great with the new style! They all look so sparkly! XD My favourite character is Britain/England with America being a very close second! I highly recommend this anime if you haven't already watched it! :)

Out of all the Hetalia dvds this one is my favorite. The animation is very fluid, almost movie quality and the stories are really funny. The ending song and dance Italy does is hilarious! However, this is the season where they have apparently changed the person who does Italy's voice. Italy's new voice is very high and he's almost impossible to understand sometimes, especially when hes excited. I found myself having to replay the dvd a couple of times to catch what he said. Once I got used to the new voice it wasn't too bad. This is also the season where they have darkened America's and England's hair. Now they have a dirty blonde look, almost orange, which is still making it hard for me to adjust to. Especially on England since he's my favorite. Otherwise, this is a great dvd and one I would recommend to any Hetalian.
